headline: Fed lowers interest rates by 0.25 percentage points in third straight cut
summary: The Federal Reserve is grappling with economic issues including higher inflation and a slowing labor market.

headline: ADP®'s New Save4Retirement Pooled Employer Plan Cuts Cost and Complexity
summary: ADP (Nasdaq: ADP) today launched the Save4Retirement Pooled Employer Plan (PEP), a retirement plan that allows multiple unrelated employers to join a single, professionally managed 401(k) structure that consolidates administration and shifts key administrative fiduciary responsibilities to a pooled plan provider.
